        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Download the plugin.<\/li>\n<li>Login to your WordPress website dashboard.<\/li>\n<li>Navigate to Dashboard &gt; Plugins.<\/li>\n<li>Click Add New and then Upload Plugin.<\/li>\n<li>Browse to the file, select it, and click Install Now.<\/li>\n<li>Click Activate Plugin once prompted.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n",
