        "description": "<p>A light-weight WordPress plugin to assign primary category to posts and custom post types.<\/p>\n<h3>How to Use<\/h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Browse to any post or custom post type in WordPress admin.<\/li>\n<li>Check the taxonomies that you want to assign to it.<\/li>\n<li>Select the respective primary taxonomies.<\/li>\n<li>Save the post.<\/li>\n<li>Use this shortcode to query the posts: <code>spc_primary_term_posts<\/code>.<\/li>\n<li>Use the action hook \u2014 <code>spc_display_primary_term_posts<\/code> \u2014 to display the queried posts in your theme.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n",
